{"word":"H3282 - יַעַן - yaʻan - yah'-an - Because","slug":"H3282","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יַעַן</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>yaʻan"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yah'-an"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Because"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D9;&#x05E2;&#x05DF; - ya&#x201B;an</b> - <i>yah'-an</i><p/>From an unused root meaning to <i>pay attention</i>; properly <i>heed</i>; by implication <i>purpose</i> (sake or account); used adverbially to indicate the <i>reason</i> or cause: - because (that), forasmuch (+ as), seeing then, + that, + whereas, + why."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4616\">H4616</a>, <a href=\"#/H4617\">H4617</a>, <a href=\"#/H5772\">H5772</a>, <a href=\"#/H6030\">H6030</a>, <a href=\"#/H6256\">H6256</a>, <a href=\"#/H6258\">H6258</a>, <a href=\"#/H6261\">H6261</a>, <a href=\"#/H6262\">H6262</a>, <a href=\"#/H6278\">H6278</a>"}]}